metadata.name: Gold Founding Member
metadata.description:
[NFTfolio](https://www.nftsfolio.xyz/?gn=20) is the only NFT Portfolio you will ever need, made by People with Cryptopunks, Bored Apes, Chromie Squiggles and Punks Comics, we are the ones that say GM and say it back, and we all together are the ones running this show, this is why we say WAGMI and LFG!

 Cryptopunk owners will have the Gold membership. This is our way of saying thank you and giving back to the Community that started it all. As long as you have at least one Cryptopunk in your wallet NFTfolio is free to use for you.
